\": \"Vietnamese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnamese_cuisine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnamese_cuisine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lee is one of the stars of the US gymnastics team.\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 305, \"end\": 308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9887648373637248, \"rank\": 0.010831675678510858, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 336, \"end\": 338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8639142388984341, \"rank\": 0.15431694258872378, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has brought home three medals (one team gold and two individual bronzes) from the Paris Olympics, bringing her total number of medals to six.\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She also won three medals (one gold, one silver and one bronze) at the Tokyo 2021 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 573, \"end\": 578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9979930247511859, \"rank\": 0.0019178200770711786, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lee officially ended her run in Paris after Monday's balance beam final and was asked post-performance what she plans on eating to celebrate.\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 600, \"end\": 603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9887648373637248, \"rank\": 0.010831675678510858, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"typ