tes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 21-year-old Mong-American gymnast then received a list of more than 50 pho restaurants in Paris.\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1138, \"end\": 1143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999736699013, \"rank\": 2.6330123998633985e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is some solid pho in Paris,\\\" wrote one X user.\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1174, \"end\": 1179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999736699013, \"rank\": 2.6330123998633985e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Someone get it to her stat!\\\"\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1229, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Paris has some of the best pho in the world... check-in with the large Vietnamese community there,\\\" posted another.\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1347, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1232, \"end\": 1237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999736699013, \"rank\": 2.6330123998633985e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1303, \"end\": 1313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnamese_cuisine\", \"score\": 0.9997189780953454, \"rank\": 0.0002782926145324704, \"text\": \"Vietnamese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnamese_cuisine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnamese_cuisine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"France is home to the oldest Vietnamese community outside of Vietnam.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\"